{{iPhone系列}}
'''iPhone'''是[[蘋果公司|蘋果公司]]研发及销售的[[智能手机|智能手机]]系列，搭載該公司研發的[[iOS|iOS]][[行動作業系統|行動作業系統]]<ref name="Engadget1">{{Cite web |title=iPhone OS 4 renamed iOS 4, launching June 21 with 1500 new features |url=http://www.engadget.com/2010/06/07/iphone-os-4-renamed-ios-gets-1500-new-features/ |accessdate=2013-04-26 |date=2010-06-07 |last=Patel |first=Nilay |publisher=[[Engadget|Engadget]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130618061616/http://www.engadget.com/2010/06/07/iphone-os-4-renamed-ios-gets-1500-new-features/ |archivedate=2013-06-18 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。[[iPhone_(第一代)|第一代iPhone]]於2007年1月9日由时任蘋果公司[[CEO|CEO]][[史蒂夫·乔布斯|史蒂夫·乔布斯]]發表<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.macworld.com/article/1054769/iphone.html |title=Apple unveils iPhone |author=Honan, Mathew |date=2007-01-09 |work=[[Macworld|Macworld]] |accessdate=2012-09-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120925200810/http://www.macworld.com/article/1054769/iphone.html |archivedate=2012-09-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並在同年6月29日正式發售<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.macworld.com/article/54769/2007/01/iphone.html |title=Apple unveils iPhone |author=Honan, Mathew |date=2007-01-09 |work=[[Macworld|Macworld]] |accessdate=2008-04-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080415223141/http://www.macworld.com/article/54769/2007/01/iphone.html |archivedate=2008-04-15 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{En icon}}{{Cite news |url=http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2007/01/09iphone.html |title=Apple Reinvents the Phone with iPhone |date=2007-01-09 |publisher=MACWORLD |accessdate=2014-04-27 |location=SAN FRANCISCO |language=en |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110608084440/http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2007/01/09iphone.html |archivedate=2011-06-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。最新發表的iPhone手机是iPhone 13系列，包括[[IPhone_13|iPhone 13、iPhone 13 mini]]、[[IPhone_13_Pro|iPhone 13 Pro以及iPhone 13 Pro Max]]，该系列于2021年9月14日正式对外发表。

iPhone运行由蘋果公司研發的iOS操作系统（原名iPhone OS）<ref name="pogueFAQ2">{{Cite news |url=http://pogue.blogs.nytimes.com/2007/01/13/ultimate-iphone-faqs-list-part-2/ |title=Ultimate iPhone FAQs list, Part 2 |last=Pogue |first=David |date=2007-01-13 |work=The New York Times |accessdate=2008-06-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080512034405/http://pogue.blogs.nytimes.com/2007/01/13/ultimate-iphone-faqs-list-part-2/ |archivedate=2008-05-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="VersatileFlash">{{Cite news |url=http://www.macworld.co.uk/ipod-itunes/news/index.cfm?newsid=16927 |title=Macworld Expo: Optimised OS X sits on 'versatile' flash |last=Haslam |first=Karen |date=2007-01-12 |publisher=[[Macworld|Macworld UK]] |accessdate=2007-01-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070113140529/http://www.macworld.co.uk/ipod-itunes/news/index.cfm?newsid=16927 |archivedate=2007-01-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="IhnatkoPerfect">{{Cite news |url=http://www.suntimes.com/technology/ihnatko/215441,CST-FIN-Andy18.article |title=You could call iPhone perfect |last=Ihnatko |first=Andy |date=2007-01-18 |publisher=[[Chicago_Sun-Times|Chicago Sun-Times]] |accessdate=2007-01-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070121100741/http://www.suntimes.com/technology/ihnatko/215441,CST-FIN-Andy18.article |archivedate=2007-01-21 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，其自带由苹果公司开发的应用程序，并支持通过[[App_Store_(iOS/iPadOS)|App Store]]来下载第三方程序。苹果公司通过在线更新服务或iTunes为iPhone提供免费更新<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2015/09/09iOS-9-Available-as-a-Free-Update-for-iPhone-iPad-iPod-touch-Users-September-16/ |title=iOS 9 Available as a Free Update for iPhone, iPad & iPod touch Users September 16 |newspaper=Apple Newsroom |accessdate=2018-08-05 |language=en-US |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171230060204/https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2015/09/09iOS-9-Available-as-a-Free-Update-for-iPhone-iPad-iPod-touch-Users-September-16/ |archive-date=2017-12-30 }}</ref>。

iPhone所採用的多點觸控技術以及其友好的使用界面使得该系列产品大获成功，同時也對其他智能手机的設計產生了深遠影響。美國時代周刊將iPhone称為“2007年的年度發明”。截止到2020年，iPhone的銷量超過了22億台。iPhone的成功使得蘋果公司成為全球最有價值的[[上市公司|上市公司]]之一。

==歷史==
苹果公司參考[[iMac|iMac]]的命名方式，将旗下智能手機产品命名为「iPhone」。

==== 研发阶段 ====
2004年，[[蘋果公司|蘋果公司]]召集1,000多名內部員工組成iPhone研发團隊，该项目被命名為“紫色项目”（{{lang-en|Project Purple}}）<ref name="RWW12">{{Cite web |title=4 Real Secrets We've Learned So Far About Apple |url=http://www.readwriteweb.com/mobile/2012/08/4-real-secrets-weve-learned-so-far-about-apple.php |accessdate=2012-10-25 |author=Dan Rowinski |date=2012-08-07 |publisher=Readwriteweb.com |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120808131222/http://www.readwriteweb.com/mobile/2012/08/4-real-secrets-weve-learned-so-far-about-apple.php |archivedate=2012-08-08 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，其中包括iPhone的幕後設計師[[乔纳森·埃维|乔纳森·埃维]]<ref>Gladwell, Malcolm（November 14, 2011）. [http://www.newyorker.com/reporting/2011/11/14/111114fa_fact_gladwell?currentPage=2 "The Tweaker: The real genius of Steve Jobs."] {{Wayback|url=http://www.newyorker.com/reporting/2011/11/14/111114fa_fact_gladwell?currentPage=2 |date=20130308210758 }} ''[[The_New_Yorker|The New Yorker]]''. p. 2</ref>。當時蘋果公司CEO [[史蒂夫·喬布斯|史蒂夫·喬布斯]] 的重點從原本的平板電腦轉向至手機<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://mobile-review.com/articles/2010/iphone-history3-en.shtml |title=Apple's Phone: From 1980s' Sketches to iPhone. Part 3 |last=Murtazin |first=Eldar |date=2010-06-20 |publisher=Mobile-review |accessdate=2011-03-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110511134715/http://mobile-review.com/articles/2010/iphone-history3-en.shtml |archivedate=2011-05-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。蘋果公司与美国电信运营商[[AT&T|AT&T]]公司秘密合作制造一些設備<ref name="CNN secrets">{{Cite news |url=http://money.cnn.com/2007/01/10/commentary/lewis_fortune_iphone.fortune/index.htm |title=How Apple kept its iPhone secrets |last=Lewis |first=Peter |date=2007-01-12 |publisher=[[CNN|CNN Money]] |accessdate=2009-01-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081210110636/http://money.cnn.com/2007/01/10/commentary/lewis_fortune_iphone.fortune/index.htm |archivedate=2008-12-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.wired.com/gadgets/wireless/magazine/16-02/ff_iphone |title=The Untold Story: How the iPhone Blew Up the Wireless Industry |last=Vogelstein |first=Fred |date=2008-01-09 |work=Wired News |accessdate=2008-01-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080509154531/http://www.wired.com/gadgets/wireless/magazine/16-02/ff_iphone |archivedate=2008-05-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>—當時的AT&T公司給予蘋果公司巨额投资以及高度的研发自由度，在30個月動用約$150,000,000美元的资金<ref name="Wired_Untold">{{Cite news |url=http://www.wired.com/gadgets/wireless/magazine/16-02/ff_iphone?currentPage=all |title=The Untold Story: How the iPhone Blew Up the Wireless Industry |date=2008-01-09 |work=[[Wired_(magazine)|Wired]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081223160607/http://www.wired.com/gadgets/wireless/magazine/16-02/ff_iphone?currentPage=all |archivedate=2008-12-23 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2013-10-17 }}</ref>。作為交換條件，蘋果公司保證在4年期限內，[[美國|美國]]出售的iPhone手机將交由AT&T公司獨家發售<ref name="#1">{{Cite web |title=AT&T remains sole iPhone carrier in US, revenue sharing axed (Updated) |url=http://arstechnica.com/apple/news/2008/06/att-remains-sole-iphone-carrier-in-us-revenue-sharing-axed.ars |accessdate=2011-05-04 |date=2008-06-09 |last=Cheng |first=Jacqui |publisher=Ars Technica |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110607170600/http://arstechnica.com/apple/news/2008/06/att-remains-sole-iphone-carrier-in-us-revenue-sharing-axed.ars |archivedate=2011-06-07 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

随后，蘋果公司否決了「設計委員會」的方法，拒絕替[[Motorola|Motorola]] ROKR E1生產<ref>[http://iphone5buzz.org/2011/11/before-the-iphone-there-was-the-rokr/ Before the iPhone there was ROKR] {{Wayback|url=http://iphone5buzz.org/2011/11/before-the-iphone-there-was-the-rokr/ |date=20130815202802 }} [http://iphone5buzz.org iphone5 buzz] {{Wayback|url=http://iphone5buzz.org/ |date=20131017170520 }}. Retrieved November 26, 2011.</ref>。相反，Cingular则給予蘋果公司充分的自由去研發iPhone<ref name="CNN secrets" /><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.wired.com/gadgets/wireless/magazine/16-02/ff_iphone |title=The Untold Story: How the iPhone Blew Up the Wireless Industry |last=Vogelstein |first=Fred |date=2008-01-09 |work=[[Wired_(magazine)|Wired]] |accessdate=2008-01-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080509154531/http://www.wired.com/gadgets/wireless/magazine/16-02/ff_iphone |archivedate=2008-05-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，甚至向蘋果公司支付它們每月服務收入的一部分（直到[[iPhone_3G|iPhone 3G]]问世）<ref name="#1"/>，以此来交換四年的[[美國|美國]]獨家銷售權。

==== iPhone上市 ====
[[File:Waiting_for_iPhones_NYC.jpg|thumb]]發售的消費者。]]
2007年1月9日，[[iPhone_(第一代)|第一代iPhone]]在[[三藩市|三藩市]]{{link-en|馬士孔尼會展中心|Moscone Center}}举办的 Macworld 2007中发布，美国西海岸時間2007年6月29日18時正式在[[美國|美國]]發售，全美的 [[Apple_Store|Apple Store]] 外有數百名粉絲提早排隊进行抢购。<ref name="AppleQ32007">{{Cite press release |url=http://images.apple.com/pr/pdf/q307data_sum.pdf |title=Apple Inc. Q3 2007 Unaudited Summary Data |accessdate=2008-06-06 |date=2007-07-25 |format=PDF |publisher=Apple Inc. |quote=Consists of iPhones and Apple-branded and third-party iPhone accessories. |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080529133618/http://images.apple.com/pr/pdf/q307data_sum.pdf |archivedate=2008-05-29 }}</ref>。由於剛推出的iPhone上市後引發抢购熱潮，部分媒體甚至称其為「上帝手機」<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/10005038 |title=Speculation that Apple may launch touchscreen 'iSlate' |author=Iain Mackenzie |date=2010-01-26 |publisher=BBC |accessdate=2011-09-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120314061447/http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/10005038 |archivedate=2012-03-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.economist.com/node/9443542 |title=Where would Jesus queue? |date=2007-07-05 |work=The Economist |accessdate=2011-09-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111001115048/http://www.economist.com/node/9443542 |archivedate=2011-10-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。第一代iPhone於2007年11月在英國、法國及德國正式發售，而愛爾蘭及奧地利則是在2008年的春季发售<ref name="iPhone 3G launch countries">{{Cite web |title=Initial iPhone 3G Country Availability List |url=http://ipod.about.com/od/iphone3g/a/iphone_3g_rel.htm |accessdate=2009-01-11 |last=Costello |first=Sam |publisher=about.com |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68DydpY9e?url=http://ipod.about.com/od/iphone3g/a/iphone_3g_rel.htm |archivedate=2012-06-06 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="3G_countries">{{Cite web |title=iPhone 3G Coming to countries everywhere |url=http://www.apple.com/iphone/countries/ |accessdate=2009-04-12 |publisher=[[Apple_Inc.|Apple]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080721021512/http://www.apple.com/iphone/countries/ |archivedate=2008-07-21 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

2008年7月11日，蘋果公司在全球22個國家及地區正式發售[[iPhone3G|iPhone3G]]，其中包括原有的6個国家和地區<ref name="iPhone 3G launch countries">{{Cite web |title=Initial iPhone 3G Country Availability List |url=http://ipod.about.com/od/iphone3g/a/iphone_3g_rel.htm |accessdate=2009-01-11 |last=Costello |first=Sam |publisher=about.com |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68DydpY9e?url=http://ipod.about.com/od/iphone3g/a/iphone_3g_rel.htm |archivedate=2012-06-06 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

2009年6月8日，蘋果公司宣布推出[[iPhone_3GS|iPhone 3GS]]，合约版iPhone預計在6月，7月或8月的下旬推出。2009年6月19日在[[美國|美國]]、[[加拿大|加拿大]]和[[歐洲|歐洲]]主要國家推出。很多用户對iPhone的成本提出異議<ref name="NPD demographics">{{Cite web |title=iPhone 3G Price Decrease Addresses Key Reason Consumers Exhibit Purchase Resistance |url=http://www.npd.com/press/releases/press_090622.html |accessdate=2009-06-27 |date=2009-06-22 |publisher=[[NPD_Group|NPD Group]] |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090626074446/http://www.npd.com/press/releases/press_090622.html |archive-date=2009-06-26 }}</ref>。iPhone 3GS的內部結構與第一代相似，但增加了一些模塊，例如 [[3G網絡|3G網絡]] 、 [[全球衛星定位系统|全球衛星定位系统]] 等。

2008年第四季度，iPhone的总销量超越了 [[黑莓手机|黑莓手机]] ，成為世界第三大手機製造商，僅次於[[諾基亞|諾基亞]]及[[三星電子|三星]]<ref>{{Cite web |title=Apple iPhone 3G sales surpass RIM's Blackberry |url=http://www.appleinsider.com/articles/08/10/21/apple_iphone_3g_sales_surpass_rims_blackberry.html |date=2008-10-21 |publisher=AppleInsider |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081022214401/http://www.appleinsider.com/articles/08/10/21/apple_iphone_3g_sales_surpass_rims_blackberry.html |archivedate=2008-10-22 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2012-09-08 }}</ref>。

2009年，蘋果公司与中国电信运营商[[中國聯通|中國聯通]]達成協議，中國聯通获得iPhone在中國的銷售權<ref name="=联通版苹果iPhone">{{Cite news |url=http://tele.pconline.com.cn/wcdma/news/0910/1878816.html |title=联通版苹果iPhone 中国正式开始销售! |date=2009-10-30 |publisher=太平洋电脑网 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121029122022/http://tele.pconline.com.cn/wcdma/news/0910/1878816.html |archivedate=2012-10-29 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2012-09-09 }}</ref>，10月30日，聯通版iPhone 3G正式在[[北京|北京]][[世貿天階|世貿天階]]发售<ref name="=联通iPhone发售引PConline编辑部口水战">{{Cite news |url=http://mobile.pconline.com.cn/dclub/0910/1879515.html |title=联通iPhone发售引PConline编辑部口水战 |date=2009-10-31 |publisher=太平洋电脑网 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121029122028/http://mobile.pconline.com.cn/dclub/0910/1879515.html |archivedate=2012-10-29 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2012-09-09 }}</ref>。

2010年6月7日，喬布斯在[[苹果全球开发者大会|WWDC]]中發布[[iPhone_4|iPhone 4]]，该机一经推出，即收获了用户的一致好评。[[iPhone_4|iPhone 4]]以其极高的设计水准，得到了许多年轻用户的青睞<ref name="Nielsen demographics" />。

2010年，时任苹果公司CEO乔布斯召开新闻发布会，对“天线门”事件做出正面回应。

