iPhone主螢幕畫面是建基於[[圖形使用者界面|圖形使用者界面]]，可用的應用程式以圖形化列表顯示，通常每次只运行一个程序。大多数情况下，iOS与苹果服务密不可分，譬如Apple Notification Service、App Store与iCloud。

=== 设计理念 ===
iOS7之前，iPhone上的iOS采用拟物化的设计，系统中有大量的高光阴影的元素，其目的是为了降低用户的学习和使用成本。

在iOS7及以后，系统中的许多元素都略微透明和模糊，其目的是为了突出主要信息，提升用户的使用效率。

=== 通话 ===
iPhone支援電話會議、暫停通話、來電顯示、合併通話等功能，並整合iPhone與其他網絡功能，例如音樂播放時接到來電，此時音樂淡出，並於通話結束後音樂繼續播放。

近距感應器會因通話時臉部貼近電話時關閉屏幕和觸感電路，以節省電源並防止無意觸碰。在iPhone4之前的型號並不支援視像通話或視像會議<ref>{{Cite web |title=Mirror-based video conferencing developed for iPhone |url=http://www.engadget.com/2007/08/13/mirror-based-video-conferencing-developed-for-iphone/ |accessdate=2009-12-20 |date=2007-09-13 |last=Melanson |first=Donald |work=[[Engadget|Engadget]] |publisher=[[AOL|AOL]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100202022452/http://www.engadget.com/2007/08/13/mirror-based-video-conferencing-developed-for-iphone/ |archivedate=2010-02-02 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，後來蘋果公司於iPhone 4的設計上加裝一個前置鏡頭，才開始支援視像通話<ref>{{Cite web |title=Mirror-based video conferencing developed for iPhone |url=http://www.engadget.com/2007/08/13/mirror-based-video-conferencing-developed-for-iphone/ |accessdate=2009-12-20 |date=2007-09-13 |last=Melanson |first=Donald |publisher=[[Engadget|Engadget]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100202022452/http://www.engadget.com/2007/08/13/mirror-based-video-conferencing-developed-for-iphone/ |archivedate=2010-02-02 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。iPhone 4發布後，蘋果公司推出[[FaceTime|FaceTime]]視像通話應用程式<ref>{{Cite web |title=Apple – iPhone 4 – One-tap video calling with FaceTime on iPhone 43 |url=http://www.apple.com/iphone/features/facetime.html |accessdate=2010-06-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100611002126/http://www.apple.com/iphone/features/facetime.html |archivedate=2010-06-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，讓iPhone用户利用[[Wi-Fi|Wi-Fi]]或數據網絡進行視像通話。初時僅支援通過第三方應用程式的語音撥號<ref>{{Cite web |title=Review: iPhone voice dialers |url=http://www.macworld.com/article/137421/2008/12/voicedialers.html |accessdate=2009-05-09 |date=2008-12-12 |last=Tessler |first=Franklin |work=Macworld |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090523170943/http://www.macworld.com/article/137421/2008/12/voicedialers.html |archivedate=2009-05-23 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。Siri和语音控制可讓用戶語音說出聯絡人姓名或電話號碼並直接撥號打出<ref name="Voice_Control">{{Cite web |title=iPhone: Make calls and play music using voice control |url=http://www.apple.com/iphone/iphone-3g-s/voice-control.html |accessdate=2009-06-10 |date=2009-06-10 |publisher=Apple Inc. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090610213018/http://www.apple.com/iphone/iphone-3g-s/voice-control.html |archivedate=2009-06-10 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。iPhone還包括語音信箱功能（某些國家或地區適用）<ref name="VV_abroad">{{Cite web |title=iPhone 3G carriers, Apple vary on Visual Voicemail |url=http://www.ilounge.com/index.php/news/comments/iphone-3g-carriers-apple-vary-on-visual-voicemail |accessdate=2009-05-24 |date=2008-06-11 |last=Starrett |first=Charles |publisher=[[iLounge|iLounge]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090613074505/http://www.ilounge.com/index.php/news/comments/iphone-3g-carriers-apple-vary-on-visual-voicemail |archivedate=2009-06-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，讓用戶只要直接查看屏幕上的語音留言清單，而不需致電語音信箱進行操作。

2007年9月5日，蘋果公司在[[美國|美國]]推出音樂[[鈴聲|鈴聲]]，用戶能夠從歌曲中自行製作鈴聲，或從iTunes商店以小額額外費用就能購買。歌曲可以從一首歌曲中任何部分抽出來，長度為3至30秒<ref>{{Cite web |title=Apple Unveils the iTunes Wi-Fi Music Store |url=http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2007/09/05itunes.html |accessdate=2009-05-24 |date=2007-11-05 |publisher=Apple Inc. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090423162242/http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2007/09/05itunes.html |archivedate=2009-04-23 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，可以加入淡入及淡出效果，當循環播放時可設置半秒至5秒的停頓，或是循環播放。所有定製可於iTunes中<ref>{{Cite press release |url=http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2007/09/05itunes.html |title=Apple Unveils the iTunes Wi-Fi Music Store |date=2007-11-05 |publisher=Apple Inc. |accessdate=2009-05-24 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090423162242/http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2007/09/05itunes.html |archivedate=2009-04-23 }}</ref>或以蘋果公司的[[GarageBand|GarageBand]] 4.1.1或以上版本中完成製作（僅用於[[Mac_OS_X|Mac OS X]]）<ref name="GarageBand1">{{Cite web |title=How to create custom ringtones in GarageBand 4.1.1 |url=http://docs.info.apple.com/article.html?artnum=307108 |accessdate=2007-12-15 |publisher=Apple Inc. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071215060626/http://docs.info.apple.com/article.html?artnum=307108 |archivedate=2007-12-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，第三方應用程式也能達到<ref name="third party ringtones">{{Cite news |url=http://www.wired.com/software/coolapps/news/2007/09/ringtone_hacks |title=How to Make Custom IPhone Ringtones Without Paying Apple $2 |last=Gilbertson |first=Scott |date=2007-09-12 |work=[[Wired_(magazine)|Wired]] |accessdate=2008-03-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080516092956/http://www.wired.com/software/coolapps/news/2007/09/ringtone_hacks |archivedate=2008-05-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2012年9月19日發布[[iOS_6|iOS 6]]，蘋果公司新增用戶能選擇拒絕來電的功能，他們可以選擇以訊息回覆，或設定提醒功能於稍後時間回覆<ref>{{Cite web |title=iOS 6 Preview |url=http://www.apple.com/ios/ios6/ |accessdate=2012-06-11 |publisher=Apple Inc. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120613065611/http://www.apple.com/ios/ios6/ |archivedate=2012-06-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

iPhone 7通话时被爆会有电流声，引起了用户的诟病。<ref>{{Cite web |title=iPhone 7 Plus频现电流声噪音 苹果同意退货 |url=http://finance.sina.com.cn/roll/2016-09-20/doc-ifxvyrit2910245.shtml |accessdate=2018-08-05 |work=finance.sina.com.cn |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180805203159/http://finance.sina.com.cn/roll/2016-09-20/doc-ifxvyrit2910245.shtml |archive-date=2018-08-05 }}</ref>

=== 多媒體 ===
iPhone提供Apple Music三个月的免费试用<ref>{{Cite web |title=Apple Music 上手：要收听有两个条件 |url=http://daily.zhihu.com/story/4836023 |accessdate=2018-08-05 |work=daily.zhihu.com |language=zh-CN |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180806024442/https://daily.zhihu.com/story/4836023 |archive-date=2018-08-06 }}</ref>，支援AAC、MP3、AAX、WAV等格式的音樂及MP4影片格式的输入，而用戶需要透過iTunes才能把電腦的多媒體檔案傳送至iPhone。除了播放列表外，所有選項都是按字母順序排列。

蘋果公司允許用戶直接從[[iTunes_Store|iTunes Store]]購買和下載正版音樂到他們的iPhone，或付费订阅Apple Music。

苹果截止到2018年7月，有两款官方耳机产品，一款是有线耳机[[Earpods|Earpods]]，一款是无线耳机[[AirPods|Airpods]]，还有一款是针对没有耳机孔的iPhone机型推出的Lightning接口的Earpods。

iPhone 5s及后续机型且运行至少iOS11.4系统的手机可以将Apple Music上的音乐放到HomePod上收听（中国大陆版HomePod需要至少IOS12系统的手机）。

=== 通讯与网络 ===
第一代iPhone能夠連接[[Wi-Fi|Wi-Fi]]或以[[2G|2G]]和[[2.75G|2.75G]]（[[GSM|GSM]]或[[EDGE|EDGE]]）網絡連上互聯網。[[iPhone_3G|iPhone 3G]]推出時支援第三代流動通訊[[UMTS|UMTS]]和[[HSUPA|HSUPA]] 3.6<ref>{{Cite web |title=Apple's Joswiak: iPhone 3G Runs Fast HSDPA 3.6, Not Slower 1.8 |url=http://www.gearlog.com/2008/07/apples_joswiak_iphone_3g_runs.php |accessdate=2008-10-12 |publisher=Gearlog |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081004215201/http://www.gearlog.com/2008/07/apples_joswiak_iphone_3g_runs.php |archivedate=2008-10-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[iPhone_3GS|iPhone 3GS]]及[[iPhone_4|iPhone 4]]支援[[HSUPA|HSUPA]] 7.2<ref name="Macworld_3G_S">{{Cite web |title=iPhone 3GS offers speed boost, video capture |url=http://www.macworld.com/article/141031/2009/06/iphone3gs.html |accessdate=2009-06-08 |date=2009-06-08 |last=Michaels |first=Philip |coauthors=Jason Snell |work=Macworld |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090611184330/http://www.macworld.com/article/141031/2009/06/iphone3gs.html |archivedate=2009-06-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，只有iPhone 4S支援[[HSUPA|HSUPA]]（14.4Mbit/s）。[[AT&T|AT&T]]早在2004年7月推出3G網絡<ref name="3G rollout">{{Cite web |title=AT&T Wireless introduces 3G wireless |url=http://www.engadget.com/2004/07/20/at-t-wireless-introduces-3g-wireless/ |accessdate=2008-12-17 |date=2004-07-20 |last=Rojas |first=Peter |authorlink=Peter Rojas |publisher=[[Engadget|Engadget]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090214152503/http://www.engadget.com/2004/07/20/at-t-wireless-introduces-3g-wireless/ |archivedate=2009-02-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，但喬布斯於2007年下半年指3G網絡在美國仍未有被廣泛普及，以及iPhone上的晶片能源效率不夠高<ref name="pogueFAQ">{{Cite news |url=http://pogue.blogs.nytimes.com/2007/01/11/the-ultimate-iphone-frequently-asked-questions/ |title=The Ultimate iPhone Frequently Asked Questions |last=Pogue |first=David |date=2007-01-11 |work=The New York Times |accessdate=2008-06-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080615232349/http://pogue.blogs.nytimes.com/2007/01/11/the-ultimate-iphone-frequently-asked-questions/ |archivedate=2008-06-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="#7">{{Cite web |title=Jobs: battery life issues delaying 3G iPhone |url=http://www.macnn.com/articles/07/09/18/jobs.uk.cell.carrier.qa/ |accessdate=2008-06-06 |publisher=MacNN |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080514074121/http://www.macnn.com/articles/07/09/18/jobs.uk.cell.carrier.qa/ |archivedate=2008-05-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，而且生產價錢不菲，故決定第一代iPhone不支援3G網絡<ref name=pogueFAQ /><ref name="#7"/>。在2.0更新版本中，加入一些大學或企業常用的認證系統，支援[[IEEE_802.1X|IEEE 802.1X]]<ref name="802.1x">{{Cite web |title=Apple —iPhone —Enterprise |url=http://www.apple.com/au/iphone/enterprise/ |accessdate=2008-06-11 |publisher=Apple Inc. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080721025159/http://www.apple.com/au/iphone/enterprise/ |archivedate=2008-07-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在點認的情況下，iPhone會詢問用戶加入新發現的[[Wi-Fi|Wi-Fi]]網絡<ref name="#8">{{Cite web |title=iPhone: About Connections Settings |url=http://docs.info.apple.com/article.html?artnum=306249 |accessdate=2007-11-04 |publisher=Apple Inc. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071019015540/http://docs.info.apple.com/article.html?artnum=306249 |archivedate=2007-10-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，並需要密碼加入，另外，它也可以手動關閉Wi-Fi網絡<ref name="#8"/>，它會自動按照訊號強度來排序，並在可用時選擇最強訊號的Wi-Fi網絡，而不是[[EDGE|EDGE]]網絡<ref>{{Cite web |title=iPhone: Connecting to the Internet with EDGE or Wi-Fi |url=http://docs.info.apple.com/article.html?artnum=305711 |accessdate=2007-11-04 |publisher=Apple Inc. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071011042909/http://docs.info.apple.com/article.html?artnum=305711 |archivedate=2007-10-11 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。同樣地，iPhone3G、iPhone3GS及iPhone4可以選擇[[2G|2G]]和[[3G|3G]]或[[Wi-Fi|Wi-Fi]]<ref name="3GSpeeds">{{Cite web |title=Apple -iPhone —Features – 3G |url=http://www.apple.com/iphone/features/wireless.html |accessdate=2008-12-14 |year=2008 |publisher=Apple Inc. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081215210028/http://www.apple.com/iphone/features/wireless.html |archivedate=2008-12-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

在流動數據網絡下，電郵附件及由蘋果公司和各種的網上商店每次的下載量必須少於20MB<ref>{{Cite web |title=Apple Increases iPhone Download Limit to 20 MB |url=http://www.dailyfinance.com/2010/02/19/apple-raises-iphone-download-limit-to-20mb/ |accessdate=2013-11-06 |date=2010-02-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105070101/http://www.dailyfinance.com/2010/02/19/apple-raises-iphone-download-limit-to-20mb/ |archivedate=2013-11-05 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。容量較大的檔案，經常接收電郵附件及播客，都需要在Wi-Fi網絡下載，因為這裡沒有檔案容量的限制。若Wi-Fi網絡不適用，解決辦法就是在[[Safari|Safari]]中開啟檔案<ref name="iPhone: Beat 10 MB 3G download limit">{{Cite web |title=iPhone: Beat 10 MB 3G download limit |url=http://crave.cnet.co.uk/mobiles/iphone-beat-10mb-3g-download-limit-49300138/ |accessdate=2012-08-06 |date=2008-12-01 |last=Lanxon |first=Nate |publisher=[[CNET|CNET]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121031213722/http://crave.cnet.co.uk/mobiles/iphone-beat-10mb-3g-download-limit-49300138/ |archivedate=2012-10-31 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

iPhone 3GS和iPhone 4可以結合地圖為重心的數碼指南針<ref name="Compass">{{Cite web |title=Apple —iPhone —Get directions with GPS maps and a new compass |url=http://www.apple.com/iphone/iphone-3g-s/maps-compass.html |accessdate=2009-06-08 |date=2009-06-08 |publisher=Apple Inc. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090612042234/http://www.apple.com/iphone/iphone-3g-s/maps-compass.html |archivedate=2009-06-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。蘋果公司開發一個讓用戶在iPhone上觀看[[YouTube|YouTube]]短片的獨立應用程式，它以[[H.264/MPEG-4_AVC|H.264]]編碼，需要互聯網的支援才能觀看影片。

iPhone用戶可以經常在任何地方進入互聯網，根據[[谷歌|谷歌]]於2008年的調查，iPhone是搜尋次數最多的手機品牌，超過其他品牌手機搜尋次數的50倍<ref name="GoogleSearches">{{Cite web |title=Google iPhone usage shocks search giant |url=http://www.appleinsider.com/articles/08/02/14/google_iphone_usage_shocks_search_giant.html |accessdate=2008-02-18 |date=2008-02-14 |last=Lane |first=Slash |publisher=[[AppleInsider|AppleInsider]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080218191224/http://www.appleinsider.com/articles/08/02/14/google_iphone_usage_shocks_search_giant.html |archivedate=2008-02-18 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，而內置的天氣和股市報價程式都需要互聯網的支援。

根據[[德國電信|德國電信]]的CEO {{link-en|René Obermann|René Obermann}}稱，「iPhone用戶的平均互聯網使用率是超過100MB，這是我們基本合約客戶平均用量的30倍<ref name="iPhoneDataBoom">{{Cite web |title=iPhone Data Booms at T-Mobile |url=http://www.unstrung.com/document.asp?doc_id=144563&f_src=unstrung_gnews |accessdate=2008-02-18 |date=2008-01-30 |publisher=Unstrung |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080207070137/http://www.unstrung.com/document.asp?doc_id=144563&f_src=unstrung_gnews |archivedate=2008-02-07 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。」[[尼爾森NV|尼爾森公司]]研究發現，有98%的iPhone用戶會使用2G、3G及Wi-fi數據服務，以及當中的88%會使用iPhone上網<ref name="Nielsen demographics">{{Cite web |title=iPhone Users Watch More Video... and are Older than You Think |url=http://blog.nielsen.com/nielsenwire/online_mobile/iphone-users-watch-more-video-and-are-older-than-you-think/ |accessdate=2009-06-27 |date=2009-106-10 |publisher=The [[Nielsen_Company|Nielsen Company]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090614082958/http://blog.nielsen.com/nielsenwire/online_mobile/iphone-users-watch-more-video-and-are-older-than-you-think |archivedate=2009-06-14 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。但在[[中國|中國]]方面，iPhone 3G和iPhone 3GS都沒有建構和分發給[[Wi-Fi|Wi-Fi]]網絡<ref name="Wired">{{Cite news |url=http://www.wired.com/gadgetlab/2009/08/iphone-china |title=iPhone Goes to China Without Wi-Fi |last=Chen |first=Brian X. |date=2009-08-28 |work=Wired |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100420140208/http://www.wired.com/gadgetlab/2009/08/iphone-china |archivedate=2010-04-20 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2012-09-08 }}</ref>。

2008年1月的軟件更新<ref name="Update 1.1.3">{{Cite press release |url=http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2008/01/15iphone.html |title=Apple Enhances Revolutionary iPhone with Software Update |date=2008-01-15 |publisher=Apple Inc. |accessdate=2008-12-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081215230427/http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2008/01/15iphone.html |archivedate=2008-12-15 }}</ref>允許第一代iPhone使用手機訊號塔與Wi-Fi網絡的位置進行「定位」<ref>{{Cite web |title=Memo: iPhone does not use triangulation |url=http://www.howardforums.com/printthread.php?t=1383413 |accessdate=2009-06-01 |date=2008-06-13 |last=XFF [[List_of_Latin_phrases_(E)|et al.]] |publisher=HowardForums |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110515192821/http://www.howardforums.com/printthread.php?t=1383413 |archivedate=2011-05-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，但由於缺乏[[GPS|GPS]]硬件配合，iPhone 3G之後的智能電話採用[[AGPS|AGPS]]，此技術由[[美國|美國]]營運。由於iPhone 4S支援[[格洛納斯|格洛納斯]]全球定位系統，此技術由[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]營運。

2011年1月，[[威訊|verizon]]引進iPhone銷售，引起公眾注意的是手機已可連接互聯網。在兩個美國電訊商的發展下，AT&T網絡已可同時使用電話及互聯網，verizon網絡只支援兩者單獨使用<ref name="TUAW">{{Cite web |title=Verizon iPhone Can't Handle Data and Voice Simultaneously |url=http://www.tuaw.com/2011/01/11/verizon-iphone-cant-handle-data-and-voice-simultaneously |date=2011-01-11 |last=Sande |first=Steven |publisher=The Unofficial Apple Weblog |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110115052634/http://www.tuaw.com/2011/01/11/verizon-iphone-cant-handle-data-and-voice-simultaneously/ |archivedate=2011-01-15 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2013-11-10 }}</ref>。

2013的WWDC中，苹果介绍了能通过蓝牙无线的传输文件的[[隔空投送|AirDrop]]。

2014年1月17日苹果公司发布了支持中国移动的3G和4G的iPhone 5s和iPhone 5c。此前iPhone并不支持中国移动3G网络。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.apple.com/cn/newsroom/2013/12/China-Mobile-Apple-Bring-iPhone-to-China-Mobiles-4G-3G-Networks-on-January-17-2014/ |title=中国移动与 Apple 于 2014 年 1 月 17 日起发售支持中国移动 4G 和 3G 网络的 iPhone |newspaper=Apple Newsroom |accessdate=2018-08-05 |language=zh-CN |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180805112811/https://www.apple.com/cn/newsroom/2013/12/China-Mobile-Apple-Bring-iPhone-to-China-Mobiles-4G-3G-Networks-on-January-17-2014/ |archive-date=2018-08-05 }}</ref>

