===文字输入===
[[File:IOS_Tastatur.png|缩略图]]
對於文字輸入，iPhone於觸控屏幕中內置[[虚擬鍵盤|虚擬鍵盤]]，支援拼寫檢查及改正、預測輸入字功能，和用戶能加入新詞的動態字典，iOS11或以后的操作系统Siri可以预判用户想要输入的内容。<ref name="hasAKeyboard">{{Cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2007/06/13/technology/13phone.ready.html |title=That iPhone Has a Keyboard, but It's Not Mechanical |last=Markoff |first=John |date=2007-06-13 |work=The New York Times |authorlink=John Markoff |accessdate=2008-06-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110127062104/http://www.nytimes.com/2007/06/13/technology/13phone.ready.html |archivedate=2011-01-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。橫向模式時，按鍵會變得稍大和間隔稍遠，更方便於文字輸入，但只得到少量應用程式支援。

iPhone支援多國語言輸入法<ref name="Keyboard">{{Cite web |title=Apple —iPhone —Features —Keyboard |url=http://www.apple.com/iphone/features/keyboard.html |accessdate=2008-12-15 |publisher=Apple Inc. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081215214736/http://www.apple.com/iphone/features/keyboard.html |archivedate=2008-12-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，可以輸入21種語言<ref name="Keyboard">{{Cite web |title=Apple —iPhone —Features —Keyboard |url=http://www.apple.com/iphone/features/keyboard.html |accessdate=2008-12-15 |publisher=Apple Inc. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081215214736/http://www.apple.com/iphone/features/keyboard.html |archivedate=2008-12-15 |deadurl=yes}}</ref>。iPhone可以輸入重音符號的字詞，只要按著字母兩秒便可，再從彈出的選擇中揀選適合的字便完成操作<ref name="KeyboardAlternateLetters">{{Cite web |title=Apple – iPhone – Tips and Tricks |url=http://www.apple.com/iphone/tips/ |accessdate=2011-11-11 |publisher=Apple Inc. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111103175634/http://www.apple.com/iphone/tips/ |archivedate=2011-11-03 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

=== 邮件與短訊 ===
iPhone設有支援[[HTML|HTML]]電郵程式，讓用戶把檔案嵌入電郵訊息中，包括相片、[[PDF|PDF]]、[[Microsoft_Word|Word]], [[Microsoft_Excel|Excel]], and [[Microsoft_PowerPoint|PowerPoint]]附件，還可在電話中檢視<ref name="autogenerated2">{{Cite web |title=Apple —iPhone —Technical Specifications |url=http://www.apple.com/iphone/specs-3g.html |accessdate=2009-06-10 |publisher=Apple Inc. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090612042413/http://www.apple.com/iphone/specs-3g.html |archivedate=2009-06-12 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

iPhone第一個版本的韌體，是透過[[Microsoft_Exchange_Server|Microsoft Exchange]]伺服器上開放IMAP來運作。蘋果公司也容許[[ActiveSync|Microsoft ActiveSync]]（至2010年7月）支援平台發布的iPhone2.0韌體（包括電郵推送）<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://blogs.barrons.com/techtraderdaily/2008/03/06/apple-iphone-sdk-event/ |title=iPhone to support Exchange |date=2008-03-06 |publisher=TechTraderDaily |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080311233401/http://blogs.barrons.com/techtraderdaily/2008/03/06/apple-iphone-sdk-event/ |archivedate=2008-03-11 |dead-url=no |accessdate=2013-11-11 }}</ref><ref name=releasedate />。iPhone會把電郵帳號的設定同步至蘋果公司的[[Mail|電郵應用程式]]、[[Microsoft_Outlook|Microsoft Outlook]]和[[Microsoft_Entourage|Microsoft Entourage]]，或可以本機手動設置。如設定正確，電郵程式能進入多個IMAP或POP3帳戶<ref>{{Cite web |title=iPhone—Features—Mail |url=http://www.apple.com/iphone/features/mail.html |accessdate=2009-05-16 |publisher=Apple Inc. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090423074738/https://www.apple.com/iphone/features/mail.html |archivedate=2009-04-23 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

短訊的排列模式類似於郵箱的格式，所有短訊都是把回覆對話置於同一版面中，界面以對話氣泡顯示（與[[iChat|iChat]]類似），根據每位收件人姓名排列，於同一個版面中顯示出來。iPhone內置支援電郵的轉發、草稿及把圖片嵌入一併發送功能。在1.1.3版本更新中加入支援多個收件人功能<ref name="1.1.3">{{Cite web |title=First Look: iPhone 1.1.3 |url=http://www.macworld.com/article/131616/2008/01/iphone_update.html |accessdate=2009-06-10 |date=2008-01-16 |last=Moren |first=Dan |work=Macworld |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090527203458/http://www.macworld.com/article/131616/2008/01/iphone_update.html |archivedate=2009-05-27 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

=== 第三方應用程式 ===
{{main|App Store (iOS)}}
在2007年6月11日的WWDC上，時任蘋果公司CEO的喬布斯公布iPhone將會支援第三方應用程式<ref name="Web apps">{{Cite web |title=iPhone to Support Third-Party Web 2.0 Applications |url=http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2007/06/11iphone.html |accessdate=2008-12-15 |date=2007-06-11 |publisher=Apple Inc. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081215230338/http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2007/06/11iphone.html |archivedate=2008-12-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>[[AJAX|Ajax]]，用以分享iPhone界面的外觀<ref name="Web apps" />。2007年10月17日，喬布斯在蘋果公司"熱點新聞"的日誌中張貼一封公開信，公布於2008年2月將會提供一個[[軟件開發工具包|軟件開發工具包]]（SDK）予第三方軟件開發者<ref>{{Cite web |title=Live from Apple's iPhone SDK press conference |url=http://www.engadget.com/2008/03/06/live-from-apples-iphone-press-conference/ |accessdate=2012-08-06 |date=2008-03-06 |last=Block |first=Ryan |work=[[Engadget|Engadget]] |publisher=[[AOL|AOL]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120818002615/http://www.engadget.com/2008/03/06/live-from-apples-iphone-press-conference |archivedate=2012-08-18 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

iPhone的SDK於2008年3月6日正式發布<ref>{{Cite web |title=Live from Apple's iPhone SDK press conference |url=http://www.engadget.com/2008/03/06/live-from-apples-iphone-press-conference/ |accessdate=2012-08-06 |date=2008-03-06 |last=Block |first=Ryan |authorlink=Ryan Block |publisher=[[Engadget|Engadget]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120818002615/http://www.engadget.com/2008/03/06/live-from-apples-iphone-press-conference |archivedate=2012-08-18 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。這是一個需要向蘋果公司註冊的免費下載軟件，它讓軟件開發者進行iPhone的開發，然後在「iPhone模擬器」中進行測試。
[[App_Store_(iOS)|應用程式商店]]於2008年7月11日連同預載iOS 2.0的iPhone 3G一同發布<ref name="releasedate">{{Cite press release |url=http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2008/06/09iphone.html |title=Apple Introduces the New iPhone 3G |quote=iPhone 2.0 software will be available on July 11 as a free software update via iTunes 7.7 or later for all iPhone customers |publisher=Apple Inc. |date=2008-06-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110501035135/http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2008/06/09iphone.html |archivedate=2011-05-01 |access-date=2012-09-08 }}</ref>，連同保養首次一同支援。iPhone用戶能夠免費更新。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Is the iPod touch 2.0 update worth $10? |url=http://www.macworld.com/article/134502/2008/07/ipodtouch.html |accessdate=2009-05-16 |date=2008-07-15 |last=Breen |first=Christopher |work=Macworld |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090531023348/http://www.macworld.com/article/134502/2008/07/ipodtouch.html |archivedate=2009-05-31 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。
=== Siri ===
{{main|siri}}
[[Siri|Siri]]是自iPhone 4S以后就搭载在iPhone上的语音助手，与2012年9月支持中文语音。
=== Apple Pay ===
{{main|apple pay}}
这是苹果在2014年秋季发布会所推出的移动支付和电子现金服务，集成在Apple Wallet应用中，适用于iPhone6或后续的iPhone，在锁屏界面按下home键就可以打开[[Apple_Pay|Apple Pay]]（在iPhone X及以后机型中是双击侧边按键），在中国大陆的一些城市的付费设施与一些商店支持Apple Pay。

=== 其他 ===
==== 隐私 ====


==== iCloud和iMessage ====
{{main|iCloud|iMessage}}
iCloud的前身是[[MobileMe|mobileme]]，iCloud附带5GB存储空间，能付费扩充。可以存储用户的部分第三方应用数据、照片、电邮等。
iMessage是苹果推出的即时通讯软件，要求聊天双方都使用苹果设备，不同于短信与彩信，它是免费的。
==== Handoff和Game Center ====
{{main|Game Center}}
Handoff在[[iOS_8|iOS 8]]中首次發佈，该功能可以在iOS 8及以上的任意一台苹果裝置（Mac需要yosemite或更高版本）中开始一项工作，让后继续在另外一台iOS 8或以上的苹果裝置中继续进行。[[Game_Center|Game Center]]是专门为游戏玩家设计的社交網路平台，发布于iOS 4.1，开始是作为独立的應用程式出现，后来成为一种服务存在。

==== 易用性 ====
iPhone為不同人士提供一個[[無障礙環境|無障礙環境]]，例如可以把文字放大來協助視障人士<ref name="access vision">{{Cite web |title=Apple —Accessibility —iPhone —Vision |url=http://www.apple.com/accessibility/iphone/vision.html |accessdate=2008-12-15 |publisher=Apple Inc. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110902085344/http://www.apple.com/accessibility/iphone/vision.html |archivedate=2011-09-02 |deadurl=no }}</ref>和使用[[隱藏字幕|隱藏字幕]]和外置{{link-en|TDD設備|Telecommunications device for the deaf}}來協助聽障人士<ref name="access hearing">{{Cite web |title=Apple —Accessibility —iPhone —Hearing |url=http://www.apple.com/accessibility/iphone/hearing.html |accessdate=2008-12-15 |publisher=Apple Inc. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081215224201/http://www.apple.com/accessibility/iphone/hearing.html |archivedate=2008-12-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。iPhone 3GS亦有為視障人士而設的黑底白字的模式、縮放功能、[[VoiceOver|VoiceOver]]（[[屏幕閱讀器|屏幕閱讀器]]）、為聽障人士而設的[[單聲道|單聲道]]功能（適用於單耳有限聽力人士）<ref>{{Cite web |title=Apple —iPhone —Accessibility |url=http://www.apple.com/iphone/iphone-3g-s/accessibility.html |accessdate=2009-06-08 |date=2009-06-08 |publisher=Apple Inc. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090612042148/http://www.apple.com/iphone/iphone-3g-s/accessibility.html |archivedate=2009-06-12 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。蘋果公司會根據美國法例{{link-en|Section 508 Amendment to the Rehabilitation Act of 1973|Section 508 Amendment to the Rehabilitation Act of 1973|第508條}}，自願性定期發布輔助功能的模板<ref>{{Cite web |title=Apple —Voluntary Product Accessibility Templates |url=http://www.apple.com/accessibility/resources/ |accessdate=2009-07-18 |date=2009-07-18 |publisher=Apple Inc. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090720073109/http://www.apple.com/accessibility/resources/ |archivedate=2009-07-20 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

