== 知識產權 ==
[[File:IPhone_sales_per_quarter.png|thumb]]
蘋果公司就iPhone的科技提出超過200項知識產權的專利申請<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://abclocal.go.com/kgo/story?section=news/business&id=4920783 |title=Apple Options Not An Issue At Macworld |last=Ishimaru |first=Heather |date=2007-01-09 |publisher=[[KGO-TV|abc7news.com]] |accessdate=2007-01-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090206203752/http://abclocal.go.com/kgo/story?section=news%2Fbusiness&id=4920783 |archivedate=2009-02-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=iPhone —Features —High Technology |url=http://www.apple.com/iphone/features/index.html#technology |accessdate=2008-06-06 |publisher=Apple Inc. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071006005308/http://www.apple.com/iphone/features/index.html#technology |archivedate=2007-10-06 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

[[LG|LG]]指iPhone的設計是抄襲{{link-en|LG Prada|LG Prada}}，該公司的研發中心主管Woo-Young Kwak在一個新聞發布會上說：「我們認為，Prada手機於2006年9月亮相於iF設計頒獎禮上，並獲得該獎項，蘋果公司就在那時抄襲它的設計。<ref name="am">{{Cite news |url=http://www.applematters.com/article/the-iphone-lawsuits/ |title=The iPhone Lawsuits |last=Wright |first=Aaron |date=2007-02-20 |publisher=Apple Matters |accessdate=2007-06-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080505060219/http://www.applematters.com/article/the-iphone-lawsuits/ |archivedate=2008-05-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>」

1993年9月3日，{{link-en|Infogear|Infogear}}提出以"I PHONE"作為商標的申請<ref name="IPhoneReg96">{{Cite web |title=Trademark Applications and Registrations Retrieval, serial number 74431935 (I PHONE) |url=http://tarr.uspto.gov/servlet/tarr?regser=serial&entry=74431935 |accessdate=2008-06-06 |date=2007-01-12 |publisher=[[United_States_Patent_and_Trademark_Office|United States Patent and Trademark Office]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080604065843/http://tarr.uspto.gov/servlet/tarr?regser=serial&entry=74431935 |archivedate=2008-06-04 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，並於1996年3月20日已申請"I PHONE"作商標<ref name="CiscoSuesAppleOver">{{Cite news |url=http://blogs.zdnet.com/Berlind/?p=284 |title=On the eve of a new phone, Apple appears to want in on the Cisco "iPhone" trademark |last=Berlind |first=David |date=2007-01-07 |accessdate=2009-01-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070210041453/http://blogs.zdnet.com/Berlind/?p=284 |archivedate=2007-02-10 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。"I Phone"在1998年3月註冊<ref name=IPhoneReg96 />，而"IPhone"則在1999年註冊<ref name=CiscoSuesAppleOver />，自此"I PHONE"的商標被棄用<ref name=IPhoneReg96 />。Infogear的商標涵蓋通訊端子的東西，包括電腦硬件及軟件提供了一個一體化的電話、數據通訊和個人電腦的功能（1993年的存檔）<ref>{{Cite web |title=Trademark Applications and Registrations Retrieval, serial number 75076573 (IPHONE) |url=http://tarr.uspto.gov/servlet/tarr?regser=serial&entry=75076573 |accessdate=2008-06-06 |date=2006-07-31 |publisher=[[United_States_Patent_and_Trademark_Office|United States Patent and Trademark Office]] |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/651J5ws4o?url=http://tarr.uspto.gov/servlet/tarr?regser=serial |archivedate=2012-01-28 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

1998年，Infogear推出結合電話與網頁瀏覽器的[[IPhone_(Linksys)|iPhone]]<ref name="InfoGearUpgradesPhone">{{Cite news |url=http://www.cnn.com/TECH/computing/9906/10/iphone.idg/index.html |title=InfoGear upgrades phone of the future |last=Needle |first=David |date=1999-06-10 |publisher=CNN |accessdate=2007-01-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070125082144/http://www.cnn.com/TECH/computing/9906/10/iphone.idg/index.html |archivedate=2007-01-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2000年，Infogear從iphones.com的域名侵權案中勝出<ref name="InfogearTechnologyV">{{Cite web |title=InfoGear Technology Corporation v iPhones |url=http://www.arb-forum.com/domains/decisions/94369.htm |accessdate=2008-06-06 |date=2000-04-13 |publisher=National Arbitration Forum |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20000817014541/http://www.arb-forum.com/domains/decisions/94369.htm |archivedate=2000-08-17 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。2000年6月，[[思科系統|思科系統]]收購了Infogear，包括了iphone的商標<ref name="CiscoFacesiPhone">{{Cite news |url=http://news.zdnet.com/2100-9595_22-6153865.html |title=Cisco faces iPhone trademark challenge in Canada |last=Kawamoto |first=Dawn |date=2007-01-26 |publisher=[[ZDNet|ZDNet]] |accessdate=2008-06-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080424032521/http://news.zdnet.com/2100-9595_22-6153865.html |archivedate=2008-04-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2002年10月，蘋果公司在[[英國|英國]]、[[澳洲|澳洲]]、[[新加坡|新加坡]]及[[歐盟|歐盟]]申請為iPhone的名稱註冊商標。隨後在2004年10月，蘋果公司在[[加拿大|加拿大]]為iPhone的名稱申請註冊，並在2006年9月在[[新西蘭|新西蘭]]申請註冊商標。同月，一間名為「海洋通訊服務」的公司在[[美國|美國]]、[[英國|英國]]及[[香港|香港]]為iPhone申請註冊<ref name="#10">{{Cite web |title=Apple filing for iPhone trademarks worldwide |url=http://10layers.com/2006/10/apple-filing-for-iphone-trademarks-worldwide/ |accessdate=2007-01-28 |date=2006-10-17 |publisher=10layers.com |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070113014820/http://10layers.com/2006/10/apple-filing-for-iphone-trademarks-worldwide/ |archivedate=2007-01-13 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，隨後在[[千里達|千里達]]和托貝哥（西印度群島一國）入稟申請<ref>{{Cite web |title=Case details for Community Trade Mark E5341301 |url=http://www.ipo.gov.uk/tm/t-find/t-find-number?detailsrequested=C&trademark=E5341301 |accessdate=2008-06-06 |publisher=[[Intellectual_Property_Office_(United_Kingdom)|UK Intellectual Property Office]] |archiveurl=http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/20080911023553/http://www.ipo.gov.uk/tm/t-find/t-find-number?detailsrequested=C&trademark=E5341301 |archivedate=2008-09-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。{{As of|2006|10}}，那些申請只得[[澳洲|澳洲]]和[[新加坡|新加坡]]獲得通過。

2005年8月，在蘋果公司在[[加拿大|加拿大]]的商標註冊申請被否決，原因是加拿大一間名為{{link-en|Comwave|Comwave}}的公司早於蘋果公司申請的三個月前獲得申請，Comwave自2004年已售賣[[網際協議通話技術|Voice over IP]]（VoIP）設備<ref name=CiscoFacesiPhone />。

2006年12月18日，Infogear以iPhone名義下的[[網際協議通話技術|VoIP]]重新發布一系列的產品<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.theregister.co.uk/2006/12/18/linksys_launches_iphone |title=iPhone launched ... but not by Apple |last=Smith |first=Tony |date=2006-12-18 |publisher=The Register |accessdate=2008-06-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080530014313/http://www.theregister.co.uk/2006/12/18/linksys_launches_iphone/ |archivedate=2008-05-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

由於海洋通訊服務的商標註冊與蘋果公司在[[新西蘭|新西蘭]]申請時使用完全相同的措辭，所以假設他們是代表蘋果公司提出註冊商標的申請<ref name="#10"/>。

