one |last=Wingfield |first=Nick |date=2007-02-22 |work=The Wall Street Journal |accessdate=2008-06-06 |format=fee required |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080516063122/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB117211001262715655.html |archivedate=2008-05-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。後來在2012年4月，思科公司稱商標訴訟案只是一個「小衝突」，並不是因為金錢的問題，而是讓軟硬體在多種品牌產品上能有意義的溝通<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://news.cnet.com/2100-1047_3-6153339.html |title=Report: Cisco CEO calls iPhone suit 'minor skirmish' |date=2007-01-25 |publisher=[[News.com|News.com]] |accessdate=2008-06-06 |agency=Reuters |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090806210332/http://news.cnet.com/2100-1047_3-6153339.html |archivedate=2009-08-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

